query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 10 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('apache-spark',
'bash',
'c',
'class',
'cocoa',
'database',
'numpy',
'optimization',
'powershell',
'python-3.x',
'string',
'templates',
'twitter-bootstrap',
'typescript',
'unit-testing');
